_sText:
A toon village map. The early typo error made it to his final name.

Big thanks go out to:

Chizbone for yet another great nav file
Phqnix for his toon textures
Karatekaefer for the best toon skybox around.

It works great on gg deathmatch servers, and is atm very popular on our server too.

32 spawns and a fair size. Typical gg map so no buyzones unfortunately. 2 tunnels to rush the other side fast.
